sajas.core

Class AID

  • java.lang.Object
    • jade.core.AID
      • sajas.core.AID
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable

    public class AID
extends jade.core.AID
    This new AID class, which extends the JADE version, provides a means to properly set and use a platform name. Programmers should use this class only when explicitly instantiating a new AID. API methods returning an AID object refer to jade.core.AID, instead of sajas.core.AID.
    Author:
    hlc

    AID
